    "html" :
    
    
    "Various kinds of damage can be caused to steering columns in the event of accidents or driving conditions similar to accidents. In cases where the steering column shows no external damage it can be difficult to detect damage. This damage represents an unacceptable risk for the vehicle, since it could lead to failure of the steering system."
    
